text: Wilelm cing gret mine biscopes & mine eorlas & ealle mine þegenas on þam sciran ðaer mine preostas on sancte Paules mynstre habbað land ine freondlice.

And ic cyþe eow þæt ic wille þæt hig beon heora saca & heora socna worþe & tolles & teames & infangenes ðeofas binnan tide and buten swa full & swa forð swa ic hafedan on æniges cyngees dæge fyrmest on eallen þingan binnan porte hand buten.
And ic nelle geþafian þæt heom ænig mann æt ænigean þingan ænige unlage beode be minan frendscipe.
